Install mc client -
  (for Mac using brew) -  brew install minio/stable/mc
  (for Windows using choco) - choco install minio-client

Note - Please make sure mc.exc file is present in 'C:\Windows\System32'


Verify installation - 

    mc --version

Add local MinIO server as an alias - 

    mc alias set local http://localhost:9000 minioadmin minioadmin123

If it worked, verify it using this command and it will list all the buckets - 

    mc ls local

To delete a bucket - 

    mc rb local/bucket_name

If the bucket is not empty - 

    mc rb --force local/bucket-name
